{"tid":473673,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟我男朋友係咪有嘢瞞住我？","createTime":"2017-11-19T12:40:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-19T14:17:30.000Z","uid":46015,"like":48,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1669bddf400fb2724aabea3f8b67d668e9c11623","tid":473673,"uid":46015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T12:40:45.000Z","msg":"男朋友有個好fd既同事係人妻<br />\n嗰人妻眼細樣柒皮膚差仲生左幾個<br />\n 我都信佢地純友誼 世界上唔喺男就女<br />\n直至男朋友同我坦白有一次公司聚會<br />\n佢同人妻飲醉左 佢以為嗰人妻喺我 佢錫咗落去<br />\n但佢話佢地之間無嘢 我開始懷疑同留意哩嗰人<br />\n岩岩我喺男朋友電話睇到男朋友同人妻有張合照<br />\n佢地坐咗喺一齊 但喺男朋友隻手搭住嗰人妻大脾<br />\n我因為咁 同男朋友嗌咗交仲冷戰緊<br />\n佢都仲堅持佢地喺無嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n究竟係咪我諗多咗？<br />\n<br />\n正評-帽事嘅 早啲分手算啦 擺明有嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n負評-無事嘅 人地都結咗婚 諗多咗唧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f130d36f9a2daac25602f4f36a754ed264c7ee97","tid":473673,"uid":100905,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T12:44:55.000Z","msg":"細樣柒皮膚差之後認錯佢係你<br />\n可能真係唔小心認錯姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a99101e75b2b77b5d93060fcfb8b584341f8bb87","tid":473673,"uid":143727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T13:02:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\">今本帽事，你多心姐。佢一定帽同人妻扑過野既</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79c7985bb499ae3ac9193b47156baa1cac86b28b","tid":473673,"uid":13187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T13:04:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細樣柒皮膚差之後認錯佢係你<br />\n可能真係唔小心認錯姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a3e93678c15d628a3d4d8217d33fe6962cfc065","tid":473673,"uid":78522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201